Results.ReviewText: My new favourite coffee a friend from work recommended it and I am usually very fussy with my coffee. the taste and aroma are fantastic. I would whole hartedly tell my friends about my new find.
Results.Title: My new favourite Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I love a good coffee you can roll around the mouth, and this one literally bursts with a bold rich flavour, totally warming. The heavenly smell when you crack open a fresh jar is just awesome
Results.Title: Bold, Flavoursome, Toasty

Results.ReviewText: Amazing flavour,I taste notes of chocolate and nut a really smooth satisfying cup of coffee, better than a lot of the coffees you pay for in coffee shops, and in the convenience of your home.
Results.Title: Coffee-tastic

Results.ReviewText: This is a favourite in our house. It's a little bit Pricier but the beans dissolve quickly, the taste is strong and rich and the lovely aroma wafts through the house everytimevI make a cup!
Results.Title: Great Coffee!

Results.ReviewText: Bought this a couple of weeks ago & now drink 3 to 4 cups a day. Nescafe Gold Black tastes great because it is a Naturally Great Blend of coffee! And it comes at a very affordable price!
Results.Title: Fantastic!

Results.ReviewText: My wife bought this for me to try as she knows I prefer stronger full bodied coffees and not the weak insipid versions, this was perfect, nothing more to say as a supp away on my coffee.
Results.Title: Great taste as I prefer full bodied coffees.

Results.ReviewText: Have been buying the new packaged Nescafe Gold Black for 3-4 weeks now.  Very tasty and full of flavour, however leaves a black coffee residue in the bottom of the cup when drunk black.
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: I only have one cup of coffee at day, bought recently new Nescafe Gold Black and it 's perfect strengh for my morning wake up cup of coffee! Consistent quality as always with Nescafe!
Results.Title: Perfect strengh

Results.ReviewText: As the supermarket didn't have classic nescafe, except for caffeine free, I picked up this jar. I was so impressed by the taste, it'sdark, strong but velvety, I have become a convert.
Results.Title: Wow

Results.ReviewText: What a fantastic coffee. Rich and aromatic, this is a premium quality coffee with a real coffee taste. Very satisfying to drink and creates a great aroma. Great value for money also!
Results.Title: A really great cup of coffee!

Results.ReviewText:
Deliously delightful morning coffee. 
I've always enjoyed Gold Blend throughout my day, but need something with a little more depth for my morning cup. This ticks the box prefectly
Results.Title: Full bodied kick start to my day

Results.ReviewText: I discovered this blend of coffee a few years ago. Before I used the Gold Blend. I love Gold Black because is strong and smooth at the same time. I even take it with me on holiday.
Results.Title: Gold Black. My ideal coffee.

Results.ReviewText:
I happened to be in my store the day that there was a promotion on the new  Black.
I prefer a coffee with a strong flavour.
It is great, a flavour that I have been waiting for.
Results.Title: The coffee that I have been waiting for.

Results.ReviewText: I like to have my coffee black and have been delighted with new flavour.  I have always found that Nescafe can be relied upon for quality of its coffee and consistency of taste.
Results.Title: Consistent

Results.ReviewText: This is the nicest tasting instant coffee that I have found, which is perfect for a quick cuppa when there is no time to faff with ground - and it makes a mean coffee cake too!
Results.Title: Best instant!

Results.ReviewText:
My  wife  say's  I  drink  to  much  coffee,  but  after  tasting  this  black  I  fully
intend  to  drink  a  lot  more.  The  flavor  is  superb,  no  other  word  will  do.
Results.Title: only  the  black  will  satisfy.

Results.ReviewText: Both in our seventies my husband and I have changed from tea to Nescafé Gold Black as our morning drink.It is full of taste and gives that  you that special stimulating feeling
Results.Title: It's the drink that makes me think.

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking this now for quite some time and find it the most enjoyable and refreshing coffee on the market and I have sampled a few I can't start the day without it
Results.Title: Very refreshing

Results.ReviewText: I tried Nescafe GOLD BLACK at my friend's place, she is actally a bar proprietor with excellent reputation and I can only say this particular product is really irresistable.
Results.Title: Irresistable

Results.ReviewText: I wanted a stronger coffee as trying to take without milk. This has a lovely strong coffee taste, without being bitter, and has confirmed my change to "black" in both ways!
Results.Title: Great aroma and strong taste!

Results.ReviewText: I like my coffee with a strong flavour and Nescafe Gold Black delivers with its rich and intense aroma which lasts long after you've finished your cup -  simply delicious!
Results.Title: Rich and intense flavour

Results.ReviewText: Recommended to me by a person of impeccible taste and the coffee lives up to her.  As well as the taste the thing that really grabs you is the aroma, really really nice.
Results.Title: Loving the dark side

Results.ReviewText: Over the last year i have become a coffee snob and tend to buy ground coffee rather than instant.  I bought this however for when I'm short on time and it tastes great.
Results.Title: Deep flavour

Results.ReviewText: we usually buy Nescafe Alta Rica it's the only instant we buy,but the shop didn't have any so we bought Gold Black as a substitute,best substitution we've ever made....
Results.Title: great strong taste

Results.ReviewText: I bought this on Saturday I'm loving it, rich and full of flavour.  Will definitely buy the decaff in the range as it's such a good price for a coffee of this quality.
Results.Title: Full Bodied

Results.ReviewText: If there is one product worth paying a little extra for it is definitely coffee and this ticks all the boxes. The only instant that comes close to my espresso machine.
Results.Title: Great coffee

Results.ReviewText: I was given this as a present from my mum, she knows I am very fussy regarding coffee. I must say, she made a great choice, I am now drinking this brand all the time.
Results.Title: taste of heaven

Results.ReviewText: I recently tried Nescafe Gold Black and I'm impressed by the strong taste of a real coffee, how it should taste. I'm sorry now I've tasted black I won't be going back
Results.Title: Black Gold

Results.ReviewText: I purchased this a few weeks ago instead of my usual gold blend and i was pleasantly urpised.It has  dark full bodied taste and so smooth.Great for drk coffee lovers
Results.Title: great dark roast taste

Results.ReviewText: Thought i would give it a go, with hesitance since i really love freshly ground coffee. However, i was pleasantly surprised to find this coffee so rich and intense.
Results.Title: Intense and rich
